text: Department of the Treasury Internal Revenue Service
This obsoletes IRM 3.24.176, ISRP System, Audit Selection System.

Instructions previously located within this IRM are no longer required as stated by stakeholder due to obsoleted forms. All forms related to the instruction within this IRM are now obsolete, transcription instruction is longer needed since the process has been automated, therefore this IRM has been declared obsolete.
IRM 3.24.176 dated January 30, 2018 (effective January 30, 2018) is superseded.
ISRP Data Transcribers in Wage and Investment Division
